# CapitalCanvas Project Structure Guide

## Backend (FastAPI)

- The primary application entry-point is [backend/main.py](mdc:backend/main.py). It declares all authentication, data, modeling, and utility routes for the API.
- Financial data providers are organised inside [backend/data_providers](mdc:backend/data_providers).  The active implementation is selected by [backend/data_providers/provider_factory.py](mdc:backend/data_providers/provider_factory.py).
- Shared pydantic request/response schemas live in [backend/models](mdc:backend/models).

## Frontend (Vite + React + Tailwind CSS)

- Vite configuration and path alias (`@` â†’ `src`) are defined in [frontend/vite.config.ts](mdc:frontend/vite.config.ts).
- Tailwind & shadcn-ui setup is in [frontend/tailwind.config.js](mdc:frontend/tailwind.config.js).
- REST helpers for talking to the backend are implemented in [frontend/src/lib/apiClient.ts](mdc:frontend/src/lib/apiClient.ts).

> Use this guide when navigating the repository or adding new features to quickly locate relevant files.
